{"tid":1820252,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【流血收場】馬鞍山迎海3年跌價一成 兩房業主蝕百萬離場","createTime":"2020-01-11T12:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T09:07:37.000Z","uid":178572,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc4549a6486ea5e463b90980d8d287b514dd874","tid":1820252,"uid":178572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"樓市陷低谷，有業主3年前買入馬鞍山新樓，近日劈價賣樓，以880萬售出，比買入價低102萬，3年跌價1成。<br />\n世紀21奇豐物業黎健峯表示，馬鞍山迎海7座高層B室，實用面積569方呎，2房2廳間隔，座向西南，望開揚景。單位原叫價920萬元，放盤半年，累減40萬元，減幅4.3%，以880萬元獲買家承接，實用面積呎價15,466元。<br />\n據了解，原業主於2016年11月購入上址，當時作價982萬元，持貨逾3年至今沽售，賬面貶值102萬元，跌幅約10%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200111/60474819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200111%2F60474819&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=4b90b20b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200111%2F60474819&h=68247fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200111/60474819</a>"},{"pid":"3143352413443dffd4ea75aa1411a5ef30378838","tid":1820252,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2863ab33ba96de9d153ec505c5ad63b4dbffd0","tid":1820252,"uid":121361,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:03:56.000Z","msg":"係佢on9 3年前用900幾萬買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯當時只值800左右"},{"pid":"4e5f2d9c35848e253ae84f84910488cc1ccd2adf","tid":1820252,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"匈宅來的"},{"pid":"b5cedc7ccc85539f2